name: k4i_dashboard
description: An api that manages the k4i survey

scripts.dev: parcel watch assets/scss/k4i_dashboard.scss assets/css/*.css assets/fonts/* assets/images/* assets/js/dashboard/dashboard.js assets/js/survey/form.js assets/js/webflow.js --out-dir assets/bundles
scripts.build: parcel build assets/scss/k4i_dashboard.scss assets/css/*.css assets/fonts/* assets/images/* assets/js/dashboard/dashboard.js assets/js/survey/form.js assets/js/webflow.js --out-dir assets/bundles --no-content-hash
